RawLine: SDM_1103796056,【機關打開了，裡頭密密麻麻以艱深的文字寫著一些武學要領，這些文字非常細小，遠看竟然構成了{color=#FF0000}「勿忘祖訓」{/color}四個大字。】,【机关打开了，里头密密麻麻以艰深的文字写着一些武学要领，这些文字非常细小，远看竟然构成了{color=#FF0000}「勿忘祖训」{/color}四个大字。】

Items.mt: <[>The mechanism was opened, and inside it were some martial arts essentials written in dense and difficult characters, which were so small that from a distance they formed the four big words "Don't forget your ancestors' training". <]>.
